<html>
<head>
  <title>Reservation Confirmation</title>
  <%= render :partial => "style" %>
</head>
<body>

<p>Hi there <%= @reservation.user.name %>,</p>

<p>Your reservation for <%= @reservation.session.topic.name %> has been confirmed. If you need
to cancel your reservation for any reason, you can do so <%= link_to "here", :controller => "reservations", :only_path => false %>.</p>

<%= render :partial => "reservation", :locals => {
  :session => @reservation.session,
  :user => @reservation.user
  } -%>

<p>You can use the attached ICS file to add the session to your calendar software.</p>

</body>
</html>

